			   ------KEY-VAULT-------   [ saving the credintials securely in azure ecosystem ]

			 add a linked service--> key-vault

			 for parameterizing key vault--> home-->resource group--> create aresource keyvault--> copy the url

			 paste in the linked service base URL page --> or for another region create a parameter and add dynamic in the base url and paste the url

			 home--> resource group--> storage account resource--> access keys--> copy connection string
			 home--> resource group--> key-vault resource--> secrets--> generate and create

			 create a blob storage --> connection string -azure key vault

			 giving access control--> goto resource key-vault--> access control--> add role assignment[contributor]--> select members--> search for the blob storage-->
																																						review and assign

			 add access policy-->configure--> secret management--> secret permission--> check GET and LIST--> select principle--> select the blob storage

